+## Core Functionality
+
+This module provides:
+
+- **Module Registration**: Register application modules in the system
+- **App Configuration**: Compose applications using configuration files
+- **Interface Definitions**: Standard interfaces for building blockchain modules
+- **Framework Components**: Core building blocks for Cosmos SDK applications
+
+Currently functionality for registering modules using the [appmodule](https://pkg.go.dev/cosmossdk.io/core/appmodule)
 package and composing apps using the [appconfig](https://pkg.go.dev/cosmossdk.io/core/appconfig)
 package is provided.
 
