 provided in this go module.
+
+## Package Overview
+
+- [`appmodule`](appmodule/): Defines standard interfaces for app modules
+- [`appconfig`](appconfig/): Handles application configuration through proto messages
+- [`genesis`](genesis/): Provides tools for genesis handling
+- [`store`](store/): Defines core store interfaces
+
+## Usage
+
+```go
+import "cosmossdk.io/core"
+```
